headline: LKQ Corporation and SYNETIQ, an IAA Company Announce Strategic European Joint Venture
summary: Key Step in Europe-wide Vehicle Recycled Parts StrategyANTIOCH, Tenn., June 24, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- LKQ Corporation (Nasdaq: LKQ), today announced that LKQ Europe has entered into a joint venture with SYNETIQ Ltd., an IAA company. LKQ Europe is the leading distributor of automotive aftermarket parts for cars, commercial vans, and industrial vehicles in Europe.
